harry potter and the deathly hallows what parts made you cry spoilers i was really touched when lupin asked harry to be godfather when dobby fred and hedwig died when hermione kissed ron over the dobby comment and he kissed her back and when professor mcgonagall and hagrid thought harry had died however i only cried once when harry was marching into the forest for his death and he saw his mom who told him you are so brave believe it or not i didn't cry until i put the book down in order of the phoenix i cried hysterically when sirius died in half blood prince i cried hysterically when dumbledore died in deathly hallows i didn't cry until i was done with the book i think i was just in a state of emotional overload i just kept reading and reading and reading until i was done it only took me two days and at the end when all was said and done everything sunk in and i cried freds death upset me the most but all in all i really loved the book Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Harry Potter (character) Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix Ron Weasley Hogwarts subjects Hermione Granger Severus Snape Dates in Harry Potter Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire Sirius Black Rubeus Hagrid Order of the Phoenix Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince Blood purity (Harry Potter) Magic (Harry Potter) Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets (film) Harry Potter: Book Seven Gryffindors in Harry Potter's year Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (video game) Hogwarts Houses House-elf Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets Diagon Alley Dobby Death Eater Dumbledore's Army Battle of Hogwarts Weasley family Half-Blood Prince (character) Nymphadora Tonks Minor Hufflepuffs Lord Voldemort Potions in Harry Potter Remus Lupin Albus Dumbledore Magical beasts (Harry Potter) Sybill Trelawney Ginny Weasley Minor Hogwarts teachers Harry Potter newspapers and magazines Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire (film) Hogwarts Floor Directory Minor Ravenclaws Professor Quirrell R.A.B. Minerva M